{"tid":694662,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【獨家】一手樓空置稅以累進制徵收　政府研「反避稅」措施防囤積","createTime":"2018-06-08T13:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T11:07:50.000Z","uid":65346,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"ce46da8624a6f5536f561a1f77ca78a0914173bd","tid":694662,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:49:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/197022/%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E6%A8%93%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A8%85%E4%BB%A5%E7%B4%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BE%B5%E6%94%B6-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A0%94-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%85-%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E9%98%B2%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F197022%2F%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A8%2593%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25A8%2585%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E7%25B4%25AF%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E6%2594%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2581%25BF%25E7%25A8%2585-%25E6%258E%25AA%25E6%2596%25BD%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%259B%25A4%25E7%25A9%258D&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e9f1b4ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/197022/%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E6%A8%93%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A8%85%E4%BB%A5%E7%B4%AF%E9%80%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BE%B5%E6%94%B6-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A0%94-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%BF%E7%A8%85-%E6%8E%AA%E6%96%BD%E9%98%B2%E5%9B%A4%E7%A9%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n為打擊已落成樓宇但仍未售出單位，即俗稱「貨尾」單位，政府早前曾研究一手樓空置稅。今日（6日）有報道指，局方已決定以差餉機制徵收一手樓空置稅，對於落成後一段年期仍未出售的一手樓，或需繳交以倍計的差餉。同時，新稅項亦將「一刀切」，適用於所有空置新盤。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士向《香港01》透露，按當局的構思，若一手單位於獲批入伙紙後一年仍未售出或租出，便會被歸類為空置單位，並以累進方式徵收稅項。同時，政府亦考慮推出「反避稅（anti tax avoidance）」，以防止地產商將單位「左手交右手」避稅。<br />\n<br />\n多個消息指，政府打算利用調整差餉，以累進方式徵收「以倍數計」的差餉，即空置時間愈長、徵收差餉愈多。消息指透過修改現有《差餉條例》，行政上會較為方便。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空置」定義，消息指是由單位獲批入伙紙後的一年仍未售出或租出起計。至於會否引致有地產商將單位「左手交右手」避稅，消息指政府考慮「反避稅（anti tax avoidance）」方案，如要求發展商以市值價錢賣出或租出單位。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據了解，雖然政府對推出一手樓空置稅非常有決心，但由於內部有不同說法，故至今尚未有「拍板」方案，現階度仍停滯不前。"},{"pid":"1baa2bd039aaf2d51984796350e18c53c495b905","tid":694662,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":10,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔起哂 唔令入伙紙咪得囉 傻鳩政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb4f1e374044e5955ada25238aa660e4dd908e4","tid":694662,"uid":26553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:58:15.000Z","msg":"聽落去 呢個方案好似好廢"},{"pid":"9e52133e7b52e01958e2fc44ac7df51432b4d107","tid":694662,"uid":33730,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"有心做就係投完地起就計時啦"},{"pid":"819435a8dc60df5297075e2c35f3a3546fab1208","tid":694662,"uid":106247,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"1baa2bd039aaf2d51984796350e18c53c495b905","tid":694662,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":10,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔起哂 唔令入伙紙咪得囉 傻鳩政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"全棟都唔賣就得<br />\n想賣一半留一半咪唔得"},{"pid":"72adf0cf636d0486bf2c939130c779079c10f8f7","tid":694662,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e52133e7b52e01958e2fc44ac7df51432b4d107","tid":694662,"uid":33730,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:02:23.000Z","msg":"有心做就係投完地起就計時啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:36:28.000Z","msg":"好似澳門咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收返塊地，fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59aa3b12e764a6ba4820f3e2699a3ad942d7d1e7","tid":694662,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"175a65191f0d77dc966c049f3ffa9e224bdcf077","tid":694662,"uid":171446,"like":4,"dis